  <brief_title>Comparison in Need for Bank Blood Between Patients Undergoing Total Hip Surgery That Either Receive Their Own Blood Back or Not</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized, Controlled Trial of Retransfusion of Intra-operatively Collected Filtered Whole Blood in Total Hip Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
